    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-large wp-image-28539 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Open-Data-Project-Banner-2-1024x45.gif?resize=960%2C42\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"42\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Open-Data-Project-Banner-2.gif?resize=1024%2C45&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Open-Data-Project-Banner-2.gif?resize=300%2C13&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Open-Data-Project-Banner-2.gif?resize=768%2C34&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></p>\n<p>The more survey respondents we have, the better the data. <strong><a href=\"https://www.alchemer.com/\">Please help promote the 2021 Global NGO Technology Survey</a></strong>\u00a0in your country.</p>\n<h2>2021 NGO Technology Data</h2>\n<h6><strong>\u25b8\u00a0<a href=\"https://reporting.alchemer.com/r/560166_5fda7e95f09c94.11116135\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">All NGOs in the United States</a></strong></h6>\n<h6><strong>\u25b8 <a href=\"https://reporting.alchemer.com/r/560166_5fda7e95f09c94.11116135\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Small NGOs in the United States</a></strong></h6>\n<h6><strong>\u25b8\u00a0<a href=\"https://reporting.alchemer.com/r/560166_5fda7e95f09c94.11116135\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Medium-Sized NGOs in the United States</a></strong></h6>\n<h6><strong>\u25b8 <a href=\"https://reporting.alchemer.com/r/560166_5fda7e95f09c94.11116135\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Large NGOs in the United States</a></strong></h6>\n<hr />\n<h6><strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project-hub/\">Open Data Project Hub</a>\u00a0\u25c2\u00a0</strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project/north-america/\"><strong>North America</strong></a> <strong>\u25c2 United States</strong></h6>\n<hr />\n<p>To receive quarterly updates and analysis of the Global NGO Technology Survey data, please sign up for <a href=\"https://mailchi.mp/nptechforgood/news\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Nonprofit Tech for Good\u2019s email newsletter</strong></a>.</p>\n<h2>Open Data Project Sponsors</h2>\n<div class=\"wptb-container-legacy\" data-table-id=\"28026\">\n    <table class=\"wptb-preview-table wptb-element-main-table_setting-28026\" data-reconstraction=\"1\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-image: initial;\" data-wptb-table-tds-sum-max-width=\"267\" data-wptb-cells-width-auto-count=\"1\" role=\"table\" data-table-columns=\"2\" data-wptb-header-background-color=\"\" data-wptb-even-row-background-color=\"\" data-wptb-odd-row-background-color=\"\" data-wptb-extra-styles=\"LyogRW50ZXIgeW91ciBjdXN0b20gQ1NTIHJ1bGVzIGhlcmUgKi8=\"><tbody><tr class=\"wptb-row\"><td class=\"wptb-cell\" style=\"border-width: 1px; width: 107px;\" data-x-index=\"0\" data-y-index=\"0\"><div class=\"wptb-image-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-image-8 edit-active\" data-wptb-image-alignment=\"center\"><div class=\"wptb-image-wrapper\">            <a style=\"display: block;\" class=\"\" href=\"https://www.eventgroove.com/\" target=\"_blank\">                                <img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wptb-image-element-target\" height=\"44\" width=\"200\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Eventgroove-Logo.png?resize=200%2C44\" style=\"width: 100%;\">            </a>        </div></div></td><td class=\"wptb-cell\" style=\"border-width: 1px;\" data-x-index=\"1\" data-y-index=\"0\"><div class=\"wptb-text-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-text-3\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 70, 69); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"\" style=\"position: relative;\"><p><strong><a data-mce-href=\"https://www.eventgroove.com/\" href=\"https://www.eventgroove.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 75, 176);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Eventgroove</a></strong>&nbsp;is a one-stop platform for virtual, hybrid, and in-person events that offers event management, online fundraising, ticketing, and online storefronts for print and digital merchandise.</p></div></div></td></tr><tr class=\"wptb-row\" data-wptb-bg-color=\"\"><td class=\"wptb-cell\" data-y-index=\"1\" data-x-index=\"0\" style=\"border-width: 1px; width: 107px;\"><div class=\"wptb-image-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-image-7\"><div class=\"wptb-image-wrapper\">            <a style=\"display: block;\" href=\"https://funraise.org/funraise-free\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/funraise-free.png?resize=200%2C88\" height=\"88\" width=\"200\" style=\"width: 100%;\"></a>        </div></div></td><td class=\"wptb-cell\" data-y-index=\"1\" data-x-index=\"1\" style=\"border-width: 1px;\" data-wptb-css-td-auto-width=\"true\"><div class=\"wptb-text-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-text-1\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 70, 69); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"\" style=\"position: relative;\"><p><a data-mce-href=\"https://funraise.org/funraise-free\" href=\"https://funraise.org/funraise-free\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 75, 176);\"><strong>Funraise</strong></a>&nbsp;combines every fundraising tool that nonprofits need for success\u2014in one easy-to-use platform. Get started with free fundraising tools. Upgrade as you grow.</p></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Open Data Project Language Sponsors</h2>\n[wptb id=\"28689\" not found ]\n",
